{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"handler.apply()","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/apply","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Obiekty</a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy\"><code>Proxy/handler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><em><code>handler.apply()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/construct\"><code>handler.construct()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/defineProperty\"><code>handler.defineProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/deleteProperty\"><code>handler.deleteProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/get\"><code>handler.get()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/getOwnPropertyDescriptor\"><code>handler.getOwnPropertyDescriptor()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/getPrototypeOf\"><code>handler.getPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/has\"><code>handler.has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/isExtensible\"><code>handler.isExtensible()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/ownKeys\"><code>handler.ownKeys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/preventExtensions\"><code>handler.preventExtensions()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/set\"><code>handler.set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/setPrototypeOf\"><code>handler.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Metoda&nbsp;<strong><code>handler.apply()</code></strong> jest pułapką na wywołanie funkcji.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"692\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/proxyhandler-apply.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">apply</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> thisArg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> argumentsList</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Następujące parametry są przekazywane do metody&nbsp;<code>apply</code>. Wartością&nbsp;<code>this</code>&nbsp;jest handler.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"target\"><code>target</code></dt>\n <dd>Obiekt, na którym została wywołana metoda.</dd>\n <dt id=\"thisarg\"><code>thisArg</code></dt>\n <dd>Obiekt, który jest&nbsp;<code>this</code>&nbsp;w metodzie.</dd>\n <dt id=\"argumentslist\"><code>argumentsList</code></dt>\n <dd>Lista argumentów, które zostały przekazane do metody.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zwracana_wartość","title":"Zwracana wartość","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Metoda&nbsp;<code>apply</code> może zwrócić dowolną wartość.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Metoda&nbsp;<code><strong>handler.apply</strong></code> jest pułapką na wywołanie funkcji.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przechwycenia","title":"Przechwycenia","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ta pułapka może przechwycić poniższe operacje:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>proxy(...args)</code></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a> i <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Reflect/apply\"><code>Reflect.apply()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"niezmienniki","title":"Niezmienniki","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Jeśli poniższe zmiemienniki są naruszone, poxy rzuci wyjątek TypeError:</p>\n\n<p><code>target</code>&nbsp;musi być obiektem, który da się wywołać. To znaczy, że musi być obiektem funkcyjnym.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykłady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Poniższy kod przechwytuje wywołanie funkcji.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">apply</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> thisArg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> argumentsList</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'called: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> argumentsList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">', '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> argumentsList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> argumentsList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> argumentsList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"called: 1, 2, 3\"</span>\n                         <span class=\"token comment\">// 6</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacje","title":"Specyfikacje","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-proxy-object-internal-methods-and-internal-slots-call-thisargument-argumentslist\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '[[Call]]' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Początkowa definicja.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-proxy-object-internal-methods-and-internal-slots-call-thisargument-argumentslist\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '[[Call]]' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Kompatybilność przeglądarek","id":"kompatybilność_przeglądarek","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Proxy.handler.apply","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/apply/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_również","title":"Zobacz również","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy\"><code>Proxy</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy\"><code>handler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Reflect/apply\"><code>Reflect.apply()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"składnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przykłady"},{"text":"Specyfikacje","id":"specyfikacje"},{"text":"Kompatybilność przeglądarek","id":"kompatybilność_przeglądarek"},{"text":"Zobacz również","id":"zobacz_również"}],"summary":"Metoda handler.apply() jest pułapką na wywołanie funkcji.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"handler.apply()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"handler.apply()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"handler.apply()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"handler.apply()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"handler.apply()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"handler.apply()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/proxy/proxy/apply","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/proxy/proxy/apply/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaS